\c 261 
\pc \bd 261\bd*

\s Ninangoja asubui
\zon1 1
\zoli1 \bd Ninangoja asubui, ndiyo siku ya baraka, Siku taabu na huzuni zitakapokwisha pia\bd*\bd ;\bd*\bd  Na pamoja na Mwokozi, mbali na dunia hii, Nitashinda kumwabudu kwa milele na milele.\bd*
\b 
\zoli1 \bd Ninangoja utukufu, unangaa toka mbali, Wa Mwokozi wangu Yesu, ndiye \bd*\bd “\bd*\bd Nyota ya \bd*\bd ‘\bd*\bd subui\bd*\bd ”\bd*\bd ;\bd*\bd  Katika mapambazuko nitaona nuru yake, Na usiku utakwisha, taabu, zambi, na kuchoka.\bd*
\b 
\zoli1 \bd Ninangoja Bwana yangu, aliyenikufilia\bd*\bd ;\bd*\bd  Tamu ni ahadi yake, \bd*\bd “\bd*\bd Nitarudi kukuita\bd*\bd ”\bd*\bd ;\bd*\bd  Kuja kwake ni karibu, ndiyo, ni karibu sana, Hamu kwake inazidi, hamu ya kufika kwake.\bd*
